"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"我當時就係一次過4隻 食咗幾日粥 冇乜嘢 唔想捱兩次苦 而家諗返好彩一次過剝 唔係剝完兩隻唔會再想去剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"我拖咗兩年都未剝另外果兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc334400d3082b61ec04b2627efda966e1bcf20","tid":1995690,"uid":230817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"392a19ce79e9e9b7bcca7973ba1735149989ef8d","tid":1995690,"uid":316234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"屌而家痛緊 應該仲要隔一段時間先有得睇牙醫 連吞口水都痛 粥都唔知食唔食到 大家個時係點捱過㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T18:05:14.000Z","msg":"嗰時瘋狂食止痛藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講野都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次因為牙痛而喊"},{"pid":"560aa70757b81a3ad9be128f2fcf6b368c3561e7","tid":1995690,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5fb8be27c1fc9e196c7f53ea4e847081789a19","tid":1995690,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"理論上同實際上都可以做到，但其實係個牙醫唔敢take risks<br />\n<br />\n剝智慧齒牽涉好多神經線，落麻醉藥份量要好精準，一次過剝風險大，一般牙科診所都唔會一次過同你剝，寧願分開<br />\n<br />\n利申：當年喺菲臘牙科睇，安排入瑪麗，全身麻醉一次過剝晒4隻智慧齒＋1隻生牙瘡救唔番嘅大牙。上面啲嘢係牙醫同我講嘅"},{"pid":"2be896b572d6d06f4a9e550b3d9d1cf9106aa6c7","tid":1995690,"uid":19925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"544b531c2dc8c69273305cc1abc0658c14907d99","tid":1995690,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594d7ca95f4da661ac3bd4e5977975fe51fd7508","tid":1995690,"uid":189377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5fb8be27c1fc9e196c7f53ea4e847081789a19","tid":1995690,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"我當時就係一次過4隻 食咗幾日粥 冇乜嘢 唔想捱兩次苦 而家諗返好彩一次過剝 唔係剝完兩隻唔會再想去剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"我拖咗兩年都未剝另外果兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:52:05.000Z","msg":"唔係痛4日咁簡單, 因為開刀埋口, 又近神經線 一時時少少剌痛 成幾個月到半年<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932139a52a7be7647a4a67aaa2ac2a31f1b43059","tid":1995690,"uid":274725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"我第一次剝其中一邊上下兩隻<br />\n痛不欲生 之後半個月都想死咁<br />\n我仲好記得剝完搭車返屋企口水冇停過咁流 <br />\n之後淨係剝另一邊嘅上<br />\n仲有一粒未剝 唔敢去剝了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢粒打橫 會唔會頂到啲牙向晒另要邊 唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1b5f44b768caa1bfad7fccea8576c626cf2420","tid":1995690,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"最好隔幾日剝曬 剝完一次呢世都唔會夠膽剝埋剩低果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f5f88edad35d3e43c44723b03adde6d069fcf8","tid":1995690,"uid":53252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a24812a2a0eced4d3783652754cb391dcfbb448","tid":1995690,"uid":40926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f56eff92ddfd5bbcf8db244516c8c6179820a1c","tid":1995690,"uid":281483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93399f823281dd0b4e979a8b0eeb4a9276445ebf","tid":1995690,"uid":40926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T20:08:29.000Z","m